# receive.link routing. Use Cloudflare's CLEAN URLs as targets (/app, /home/) — referencing the
# .html filename makes Pages 308-redirect to the clean URL and loop. The app (app.html -> /app) owns
# the functional routes; the marketing homepage (home/index.html -> /home/) owns "/". A share-link
# open (/#code) reaches "/" with the code in the hash, and home/index.html's inline script hands it
# to /u (upload) client-side, so the code never leaves the hash.
/confirm   /app      200
/d/*       /app      200
/u         /app      200
/          /home/    200
/*         /app      200
